
- prepare the environment
https://github.com/igor-olikh/adk-installation

- create an .env file and set your parameters
https://developer.watson-orchestrate.ibm.com/getting_started/wxOde_setup

- run the following command
orchestrate server start --env-file=.env

- activate the local environment
orchestrate env activate local

- double check the local environment is active
orchestrate env list

- start the chat (only if you already have, at least, one agent)
orchestrate chat start


